original_title: Chikara Young Lions Cup VII - Night 2
overview: August 15th, 2009 :: The annual showcase for rookies, Chikara's Young Lions Cup tournament, continues here! The next 12 wrestlers battle to reach the finals the next night! Features the in-ring debut of Carpenter Ant. CMLL sends us two mini-luchadores the likes of which Chikara has never seen! Matches featured:  1. First Round Match: Yellow Dog vs Vokoder  2. First Round Match: Carpenter Ant vs Soldier Ant  3. First Round Match: Ryan Cruz vs Darin Corbin  4. First Round Match: Shane Hollister vs Trik Davis  5. First Round Match: Grizzly Redwood vs El Leonino  6. First Round Match: Player Uno vs Player Dos  7. Arik Cannon vs Jigsaw  8. Pierrothito vs Mascarita Dorado  9. Young Lions Cup VII Eliminator # 2: The SIx First Round Winners Battle.
title: Chikara Young Lions Cup VII - Night 2
